data.description:
Quaint corner lot home nestled on a quiet, woodsy street. Wrap around porch gives that feel of a country home, yet close to amenities. Home boasts large main floor bedroom, open kitchen and living room and large dining room. Upstairs has additional bedroom with large dormer window that would be a perfect spot for a built in window seat or take advantage of the extra room the window allows for. Loft can be built into additional bedroom and already has the double closet and large dormer window. Bedroom and loft share a full bathroom. Partial basement is finished with space that can act as a bedroom, a work out space, craft area, extra office area, you name it! With the convenience of a basement bathroom, you don't have to go upstairs to use the facilities. 
Neighborhood  with many pocket parks also has a K-8 charter school, small grocery store, and other great conveniences close by.
Things to know: radon system installed in 2022
Water softener is owned and stays with the house; seller has had annual maintenance. Buyer responsibility to refill the salt.
All window coverings and draperies included.
